---
---

<section class="about" id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about__inner">
      <div class="about__photo-wrap">
        <img
          src="/images/tetsu-island.webp"
          alt="Tetsu — MKUltraman, on a hilltop in Japan"
          class="about__photo"
          width="400"
          height="400"
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="about__content">
        <p class="about__name">Tetsu — MKUltraman</p>
        <p class="about__meta eyebrow">Digital Infrastructure · Tokyo · 10+ Years</p>
        <p class="about__bio">
          I don't sell volume. I work with a small number of organizations at a time,
          go deep on their operations, and build infrastructure that compounds over time.
          Ten years in the Japan market, across industries from F&B to media to professional
          services. If execution feels harder than it should be, that instinct is
          usually right — and it's usually structural.
        </p>
        <a href="/contact" class="about__cta">Start a conversation →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: var(--space-64) 0;
  }

  .about__inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-48);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about__photo-wrap {
    width: 280px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .about__photo {
    width: 100%;
    height: 320px;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center top;
    display: block;
  }

  .about__name {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }

  .about__meta {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-16);
    font-size: 11px;
  }
  .about__meta::before { display: none; }

  .about__bio {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.75;
    max-width: 620px;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-24);
  }

  .about__cta {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--accent);
    transition: opacity 0.15s;
  }
  .about__cta:hover { opacity: 0.75; }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .about__inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-24);
    }
  }
</style>
